data.meta_description: CET time now, get the current time in Central European Time with UTC time offset, time difference and current date in time zone.
data.text:
CET Time Now

CET is the abbreviation of Central European Time. Time zone offset of CET is UTC+01. Central European Time is 1 hour ahead from the UTC universal time. CET current date is 15th Thursday August 2024. Current time in CET (CET).

Central European Time has the abbreviation of CET. Central European Time is 1 hour ahead from the UTC universal time. It is used as the basic time standard in most of European and African countries. CET is used in such cities as Rome, Berlin, Budapest, Amsterdam.

What time is it in Central European Time now? It is 14:56:13 right now.
